snippet.title: MOTHER: Cognitive Dissonance (CogDis) Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's out! Go get it, I hope you have fun.
http://cogdis.tazmily.com

"Mother: Cognitive Dissonance" is a full-featured, fan created RPG set in the Mother series.
In 198X, after the first defeat of the invader known then as Giegue, it tells a story of his descent into the madness of Giygas and the band of aliens who once protected the Apple of Enlightenment.

This version 2.0 is heavily revised, updated, and expanded from the original.
